     H            Y.
      ** ACMR001  ******************************************
      *  PROCESS LIST OF PROGRAMS THAT USE SPECIFIED       *
      *  FILE.                                             *
      * LEC   10/06/2022 CREATE                            *
      ******************************************************
     FVVVPP10 IF  E           K        DISK
     FACMWP01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      * SYSTEM TIME
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WSDT
     I                                        1   20WSSHHH
     I                                        3   40WSSNNN
     I                                        5   60WSSSSS
     I                                        7  100WSSYYY
     I                                       11  120WSSMMM
     I                                       13  140WSSDDD
     I                                        1   40WSSTM4
     I                                        1   60WSTIME
     I                                        7  140WSDATE
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           #FILNM 10
     C                     PARM           #TOLIB 10
      *
     C           KEY01     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WHPNAM
      *
     C           *IN51     DOWEQ*OFF
      *
     C                     READ VVVPP10                  51
     C   51                LEAVE
      *
      *  if pgm uses file, and type is RPG or Blank, then compile the pgm...
     C           WHPF      IFEQ #FILNM
     C           WHSYSN    IFEQ 'RPG'
     C           WHSYSN    OREQ *BLANK
      *
      *  check to verify program has not already been compiled...
     C           KEY01     CHAINACMWP01              52
     C           *IN52     IFEQ *ON
     C                     CALL 'ACMC002'
     C                     PARM           WHPNAM
     C                     PARM           #TOLIB
     C                     PARM           WHSYSN
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEL*ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
      *-----------------------------------------------------
